

 To install webber:


 make root= /path/to/root

will install

	main config file in /path/to/root/etc/webber/webber.wbb
	webber (program) in /path/to/root/usr/bin/webber
        webber (procs)  in /path/to/root/usr/lib/webber/procs
	doc  	in /path/to/root/share/doc/webber


Defaults to:
	root=/
	
so 
	config	(etc) is /etc/webber.wbb
	webber (program) /usr/bin/webber
	webber (procs)	 /usr/lib/webber/procs
	doc 		/usr/share/doc/webber


you need to define the WBBROOT environment variable if you install
webber to a different path


setup

 After the installation, edit the webber.wbb file to configure your environment

